{"TopicId":191305,"ForumId":147,"TopicTitle":"February Threads of the Month","CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-01-31T11:03:39Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-01-31T11:03:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nThe KSP Moderation Team is proud to present\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(53,60,65);font-size:14px;text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#353c41;font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EThreads of the Month Awards, for February\u00A02020!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022a4k1egb.png?1\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002255.75\u0022 height=\u002297\u0022 width=\u0022174\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/a4k1egb.png?1\u0022\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(53,60,65);font-size:14px;text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nThis month we would like to give a special tribute to all the people involved with\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://spaceflightnow.com/2020/01/28/nasa-prepares-to-shut-down-one-of-its-great-observatories/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ENASA\u2019s Spitzer Space Telescope that will be put into safe mode\u003C/a\u003E after 16 years of stellar service discovering exoplanets, distant galaxies and star forming clouds of dust and gas. Astronomers will use Spitzer\u0027s data legacy long after the mission ends and the space telescope\u00A0will be placed in a\u00A0\u2018sun coning\u2019 attitude\u00A0that will eventually be lapped by Earth in 34 years.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E:Hailprobe::\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(53,60,65);font-size:14px;text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(53,60,65);font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nFirst up for February we have a fascinating tutorial and showcase/shareplace for the robotic parts and same vessel interactions\u00A0by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149419-servo/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022149419\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149419-servo/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Servo\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0in The Spacecraft Exchange sub forum:\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022149419\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1555985161\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/190903-bendy-tech-stock-mechanics-in-a-new-era/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(53,60,65);font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nIn keeping with the theme of an unconventional approach to design and construction\u00A0\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/38787-klond/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002238787\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/38787-klond/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@klond\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0has astonished\u00A0us with this stock KSP V8:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002238787\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1909212630\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/191069-mechanical-things-4-stroke-engine/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nIf you have ever thought that the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E needs a harbor (that includes water, helipad and rover spawn points)\u00A0\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167617-jadeofmaar/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022167617\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167617-jadeofmaar/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@JadeOfMaar\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0has released this fantastic\u00A0mod, normally part of\u00A0JNSQ:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022167617\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed2357373440\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/190893-18x-ksc-harbor-from-jnsq-v111-jan-14-2020/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nIf you ever wanted to see the constellation program in action in KSP,\u00A0\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/154577-jay-the-amazing-toaster/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022154577\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/154577-jay-the-amazing-toaster/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Jay The Amazing Toaster\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0has begun an inspiring\u00A0playthrough here:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022154577\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed6489052375\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/191264-k%C4%81n%C4%81wai-ares-to-mars/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nNext we have an amazing community space station\u00A0challenge by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/159289-jeb-head-mug-kerman/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022159289\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/159289-jeb-head-mug-kerman/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Jeb-head-mug kerman\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0and all the\u00A0contributors to this thread:\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022159289\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed4338200042\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/190947-community-space-station-challenge/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/139095-hotel26/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022139095\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/139095-hotel26/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Hotel26\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0and the Prestigious Association of Kerbin Explorers have been orienteering their way to all the best sights on the planet utilising basic navigation instructions, great design and\u00A0vocabulary:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022139095\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed5958851956\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/190112-kayak-club/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nOur stalwart pillar of the community,\u00A0\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129964-linuxgurugamer/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022129964\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129964-linuxgurugamer/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@linuxgurugamer\u003C/a\u003E, has created a stopwatch mod at the request of a\u00A0member that gives us the ability to play better and also not overcook food while doing so:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed3497829056\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/190916-18x-big-ben-stopwatch-timers-to-count-down-and-up/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nCongratulations to all for your wonderful contributions and please remember to report a thread (add the comment \u0027totm\u0027) or PM a moderator if you feel it is worthy of thread of the month.\u00A0 Special thanks go to\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/195204-fulgur/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022195204\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/195204-fulgur/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@fulgur\u003C/a\u003E, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/190611-sturmhauke/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022190611\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/190611-sturmhauke/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@sturmhauke\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0and\u00A0\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/192121-mars-bound-hokie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022192121\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/192121-mars-bound-hokie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Mars-Bound Hokie\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003Efor\u00A0nominating.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nAll winners are free to add the great new Thread of the Month badge (created once again by our very own\u00A0\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/89014-adsii1970/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002289014\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/89014-adsii1970/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022 style=\u0022color:#ffffff;font-size:12.6px;padding:0px 5px;\u0022\u003E@adsii1970\u003C/a\u003E) to their posts, signatures or have it shaved into their hair provided that 1) You are not bald\u00A02) You are not subject to any dress rules in school/at work/by family/etc. 3) The work must be done by a reputable salon with public/customer insurance. 4) You do not live in a community that discriminates against strange haircuts. 5) Pics or it didn\u0027t happen.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"zer0Kerbal","CreatedById":190933,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-01T10:42:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ncongrats to all TOTM!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Outsoldier","CreatedById":202583,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-01T17:02:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood job!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"\u03AD\u0137 \u03BD\u03AF\u013B\u013B\u03AC\u03AF\u03AE","CreatedById":197328,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-02T02:40:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCongrats!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerballingSmasher","CreatedById":195689,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-10T23:05:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAh yes, being able to not overcook food and simultaneously play KSP is a great gift from \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129964-linuxgurugamer/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022129964\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129964-linuxgurugamer/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@linuxgurugamer\u003C/a\u003E! (not sarcastic)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BR202A","CreatedById":202549,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-11T17:06:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBrilliant job\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:rep:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/rep.png\u0022 title=\u0022:rep:\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:rep:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/e